descriptor.name: My WakeUp Innovation  (Karnataka)
descriptor.short_desc: Our aim is to provide the best and pure wooden furniture along with a range of comfortable luxury mattresses. With our strong emphasis on product development innovation, process efficiency, cost optimization, and customer experience perfection, we quickly gained recognition in the market.
descriptor.long_desc: Founded in 2014 in Haryana, Wakeup started its journey as a sleep solution and furniture firm with a vision to revolutionize the Indian furniture and mattress industry. Our aim is to provide the best and pure wooden furniture along with a range of comfortable luxury mattresses. With our strong emphasis on product development innovation, process efficiency, cost optimization, and customer experience perfection, we quickly gained recognition in the market.Since our inception, we have been driven by the passion to create high-quality goods that surpass our competitors in terms of efficiency and affordability. With a vast collection of over 500 wooden furniture designs, we are committed to continuously expanding our range to cater to your diverse needs. We pride ourselves on using premium-quality solid Sheesham wood to craft the finest wooden products, ensuring exceptional quality and durability.
